---
import { FaArrowRightLong } from "react-icons/fa6";
import Asterisk from "./asterisk.astro";
---

<article class="mt-[10rem]">
	<h2 class="text-7xl san-jose text-center">OUR FITNESS CLASS</h2>
	<ul
		class="flex gap-7 san-jose text-4xl tracking-tight *:relative *:text-[#898989] justify-center mt-10"
	>
		<li>All</li>
		<li>SIGNATURE CLASS</li>
		<li class="selected">STRENGTH AND CONDITIONING</li>
		<li>MIND AND BODY</li>
		<li>CYCLING</li>
		<li>CARDIO</li>
	</ul>
	<div class="mt-12 gap-12 global-spacing grid-services-class">
		<div class="flex justify-start relative">
			<button
				class="rounded-[3rem] absolute -bottom-[9.7rem] origin-top-left -rotate-90 h-[150px] w-[500px] flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-5xl san-jose bg-tertiary"
				>BODYCOMBAT <span class="text-3xl"><FaArrowRightLong /></span></button
			>
		</div>
		<img
			class="border-8 border-light rounded-[2rem] w-full"
			src="/images/services-class.webp"
			alt="Imagen de clases"
		/>
		<div class="px-4 flex flex-col justify-center">
			<h4 class="san-jose text-6xl">BODYPUMP</h4>
			<p class="font-bold mt-4 w-5/6">
				This Barbell Exercise Targets All Of Your Major Muscles. Based On â€˜The
				Rep Effect, This Proven Formula Will Train Your Muscles Using Light To
				Moderate Weights For High Rep Exercises, Which Is The Secret To
				Developing Athletic Muscles.
			</p>
			<div
				class="flex mt-8 gap-6 items-center *:size-20 *:overflow-hidden *:rounded-full *:border-4"
			>
				<div class="border-accent">
					<img
						class="w-full"
						src="/images/services-bodypump-1.png"
						alt="imagenes de bodypump"
					/>
				</div>
				<div>
					<img
						class="w-full"
						src="/images/services-bodypump-2.png"
						alt="imagenes de bodypump"
					/>
				</div>
				<div>
					<img
						class="w-full scale-125"
						src="/images/services-bodypump-3.png"
						alt="imagenes de bodypump"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div
		class="mt-24 flex-wrap text-7xl san-jose global-spacing px-20 section-text-with-images [line-height:1.1] tracking-tight relative text-center"
	>
		<Asterisk props="right-[6rem] -top-[6rem] -z-10 text-[16rem]" />

		THE LAST THREE OR FOUR REPS IS <img
			src="/images/img-to-text-1.png"
			alt="Image user 1"
		/> WHAT MAKES THE <img src="/images/img-to-text-2.png" alt="Image user 2" />
		MUSCLE GROW. THIS AREA OF PAIN DIVIDES A CHAMPION FROM <img
			src="/images/img-to-text-3.png"
			alt="Image user 3"
		/> SOMEONE WHO IS NOT <img
			src="/images/img-to-text-4.png"
			alt="Image user 4"
		/> A CHAMPION."
	</div>
</article>

<style>
	.selected {
		@apply text-light;
	}
	.selected::after {
		content: "";
		@apply absolute -bottom-4 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-accent rounded-full;
	}
	.grid-services-class {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 150px 2.7fr 1.5fr;
	}

	.section-text-with-images img {
		@apply size-[4.5rem] rounded-full inline-block -mt-4 mx-0;
	}
</style>
